reviewText: This movie is alright! but that is all, its not extordinary by any means! it has a couple of good fights. the shamrock fight only goes a little bit into the first round, the fight is pretty much one sided. there are apearances from, tito ortiz, bill goldberg, and chuck liddel, but they are not fighting. just being interviewed. i would only sudgest you buy this used. i payed only 6 bucks for mine, and it was worth it, but i wouldnt pay more then 10.
